data.description: Best and Final offers submitted by 5PM Saturday the 3rd. Showings will be cut off by then. Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem, built in 2011, is a perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless charm. With 1544 square feet of well-designed living space, this residence offers the ideal backdrop for your family's memories. As you step inside, the spacious and inviting atmosphere greets you, highlighted by the seamless flow between rooms. The heart of this home is the kitchen, boasting dark stain cabinets that perfectly complement the tile flooring and granite countertops. Cooking and entertaining become a joy in this well-appointed culinary space. The thoughtful layout extends to the cozy living spaces, creating an environment perfect for relaxation and gatherings. The bedrooms are generously sized, providing comfort and privacy for every member of the family. The 2 bathrooms feature modern fixtures and tasteful finishes, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routine. But the allure of this residence isn't confined to the indoors. Step outside onto the large covered back patio, complete with a ceiling fan, where you can unwind, entertain guests, or simply enjoy the fresh air. The .14-acre lot offers ample space for outdoor activities and gardening. The exterior of the home is a visual delight, featuring a picturesque facade adorned with a large tree in the front yard. The combination of brick and siding not only enhances the curb appeal but also adds to the durability and character of the property. With a 2-car garage, you'll have plenty of space for your vehicles and additional storage. This home is not just a place to live; it's a sanctuary where comfort, style, and functionality converge. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful property your own. Schedule a viewing today and step into a home that's ready to welcome you with open arms. Your dream lifestyle begins here!
